44:59.087 --> 45:00.924
They have never promoted me.

45:03.412 --> 45:05.002
I'm a good sailor, but...

45:05.680 --> 45:07.737
I'm a good sailor going nowhere,

45:09.596 --> 45:10.823
because they know.

45:11.718 --> 45:12.893
How do they know?

45:13.532 --> 45:15.291
I saved a sailor's life once.

45:16.385 --> 45:18.752
He was being beaten to
death for being gay.

45:20.157 --> 45:22.416
And if I hadn't have been there,

45:22.441 --> 45:24.065
if I hadn't have stopped them,

45:25.212 --> 45:27.182
no one would ever have suspected me.

45:31.901 --> 45:33.229
I did a good thing,

45:34.696 --> 45:36.534
the bravest thing I've ever done...

45:39.963 --> 45:42.151
and I can't tell you
how many times I've dreamt

45:42.176 --> 45:44.104
about taking that moment back...

45:46.740 --> 45:48.119
and letting him die.

45:53.110 --> 45:54.790
Just so that people
wouldn't know about me.

45:55.707 --> 45:56.815
(SNIFFS)

46:32.787 --> 46:33.959
(DOOR OPENS)

46:57.907 --> 46:59.099
(SCOFFS)

47:03.463 --> 47:05.880
- You went through my stuff?
- I was going to tidy up.

47:05.905 --> 47:07.104
You touched my uniform.

47:08.611 --> 47:10.701
- I'll put it back. So what?
- So what?!

47:12.696 --> 47:14.576
I don't know why you keep it around.

47:15.311 --> 47:17.498
You never served your country.
You don't understand.

47:17.523 --> 47:19.927
No, I-I don't understand.
Look how they treated you.

47:19.952 --> 47:22.263
You have never believed
in anything except yourself.

47:22.288 --> 47:24.459
I believed in you, didn't I,

47:25.071 --> 47:27.770
- when they certainly didn't.
- Everything you gave me...

47:28.247 --> 47:31.696
the bars, the meals, the men...
it means nothing.

47:31.791 --> 47:33.380
I want my life back.

47:33.768 --> 47:36.646
My real life, my life as a soldier.

47:36.671 --> 47:38.388
They don't want you.

47:39.608 --> 47:41.287
They never wanted you.

47:41.391 --> 47:43.427
Jeff, I-I wanted you.

47:43.452 --> 47:44.709
I don't know you.

47:45.212 --> 47:47.998
I don't know what you stand for.

47:48.023 --> 47:50.474
I don't know who you are.

47:52.457 --> 47:53.693
You're a liar.

47:56.571 --> 47:58.568
You ha-you ha... you have no honor.

48:00.930 --> 48:02.904
Oh, honor?

48:03.480 --> 48:04.834
Oh, please,

48:04.859 --> 48:07.615
you're not in the Navy anymore, sweetie.

48:08.576 --> 48:10.927
You're a washed-up queer in a shitty job

48:10.952 --> 48:14.151
in a shitty condo bitching about
how you could have been someone.

48:14.176 --> 48:15.568
You're not wrong about that.

48:15.861 --> 48:18.388
When I found you that night at the bar,

48:19.130 --> 48:20.929
I was there for you.

48:21.873 --> 48:24.419
I saved you.

48:24.691 --> 48:26.560
You destroyed me.

48:29.349 --> 48:31.591
I wish I'd never walked into that bar.

48:31.616 --> 48:33.568
I wish I'd never met you.

48:37.875 --> 48:39.310
You're confused.

48:40.172 --> 48:42.388
I can see it.
No, you're-you're confused,

48:42.413 --> 48:43.962
and you-you can't even see it.

48:43.987 --> 48:46.236
I see it. I feel it.

48:46.261 --> 48:47.623
I hate it.

48:50.278 --> 48:51.724
No. I loved you so...

48:51.749 --> 48:53.951
No one wants your love!

49:25.698 --> 49:27.013
(DOOR OPENS)

49:28.050 --> 49:29.224
(DOOR SLAMS)

49:37.041 --> 49:38.091
Andrew.

49:39.610 --> 49:40.669
(SIGHS)

49:41.863 --> 49:42.865
Yes?

49:43.599 --> 49:45.115
I-I didn't hear the buzzer.

49:45.874 --> 49:47.709
I didn't want you to have to come down.

49:48.135 --> 49:50.068
I just slipped in behind someone else.

49:51.193 --> 49:52.982
You should get that buzzer fixed.

49:57.662 --> 49:59.162
(WHISPERING): Yeah, uh, I'll call.

50:02.138 --> 50:03.263
Okay.

50:09.494 --> 50:11.676
- About what you said...
- What did I say?

50:12.720 --> 50:14.037
That I needed help.

50:17.068 --> 50:18.248
Okay.

50:20.115 --> 50:21.380
How about we talk?

50:22.927 --> 50:23.990
Tonight.

50:26.310 --> 50:27.498
Sure.

50:37.901 --> 50:39.115
(STEAM HISSING)

51:04.148 --> 51:05.466
♪

51:21.310 --> 51:22.646
(PHONE LINE RINGING)

51:26.206 --> 51:27.919
- JEFF: Hello?
- I have your gun.

51:27.944 --> 51:30.771
<i>I needed to borrow it because
David's stalker's back in town,</i>

51:30.796 --> 51:32.392
<i>and I needed to borrow
it to protect him.</i>

51:32.416 --> 51:34.005
Are you out of your mind?

51:34.292 --> 51:35.959
Do you even have a license?

51:36.569 --> 51:38.693
<i>That gun never leaves the apartment.</i>

51:44.302 --> 51:47.865
All right, I'll come over
there, I'll get it off you,

51:48.309 --> 51:49.568
but I'm done with you.

51:50.397 --> 51:52.599
<i>I'm done with you. You hear me?</i>

51:52.904 --> 51:54.153
You said that already.

51:54.224 --> 51:55.404
(CLICK, DIAL TONE)

52:16.184 --> 52:17.404
(INTERCOM BEEPING)

52:22.312 --> 52:23.396
(BUZZING)

52:25.910 --> 52:27.201
Could you get the door?

52:27.990 --> 52:29.021
(SCOFFS)

52:29.544 --> 52:30.591
Are you kidding me?

52:30.616 --> 52:32.529
Well, Jeff is very
hostile at the moment.

52:32.554 --> 52:34.004
I don't want to have to
get into an argument

52:34.028 --> 52:35.115
with him in the doorway.

52:35.330 --> 52:36.365
(ELEVATOR BELL CHIMES)

52:42.130 --> 52:43.177
(JEFF SIGHS)

52:43.202 --> 52:44.341
- Hey.
- Hey.

53:01.025 --> 53:02.271
(ELEVATOR BELL CHIMES)

53:05.445 --> 53:06.849
You can't feel sorry for him.

53:06.960 --> 53:08.591
Yeah? Why not?

53:09.113 --> 53:10.224
You did.

53:10.703 --> 53:12.013
JEFF: Not anymore.

53:13.111 --> 53:14.732
I never want to see him again.

53:14.914 --> 53:17.013
DAVID: Then why'd you even come over?

53:17.388 --> 53:19.028
JEFF: He took something
from my apartment.

53:19.339 --> 53:20.584
DAVID: What'd he take?

53:21.326 --> 53:22.427
JEFF: My gun.

53:26.921 --> 53:28.107
(DOOR UNLOCKING)

53:29.409 --> 53:31.654
(PRINTS WHINING, PLAYFULLY GROWLING)

53:33.811 --> 53:34.919
DAVID: Prints...

53:35.599 --> 53:37.412
- (PRINTS PLAYFULLY GROWLING)
- Hey, buddy.

53:39.201 --> 53:40.412
Andrew?

53:42.190 --> 53:43.326
Andrew!

53:45.407 --> 53:46.895
(SCREAMING)

53:47.818 --> 53:49.560
- HUSBAND: You got it.
- NURSE: Hey, hi.

53:49.561 --> 53:50.974
Take a deep breath, kiddo.

53:50.999 --> 53:52.272
JEFF (ON ANSWERING MACHINE):
Hey, it's Jeff.

53:52.296 --> 53:53.381
I can't make it to the phone,

53:53.405 --> 53:55.054
so please leave a
message after the beep.

53:55.591 --> 53:58.068
- (BEEP)
- Hey, Jeff, it's Mom.

53:58.177 --> 53:59.576
Your sister's gone into labor.

53:59.601 --> 54:00.900
We're heading into the hospital.

54:00.925 --> 54:02.525
We'll see you there.

54:05.711 --> 54:07.748
- (BEEP)
- Hey, Jeff, it's Mom.

54:08.173 --> 54:09.248
Where are you?

54:14.334 --> 54:16.209
- (BEEP)
- Hey, Jeff, it's Mom again.

54:16.474 --> 54:19.607
So, your sister just delivered
a beautiful baby girl.

54:19.935 --> 54:22.255
She's doing well, the baby's well.

54:22.771 --> 54:25.013
DAD: Hey, kid, we're all here.
Come and see your niece.

54:25.038 --> 54:26.052
Come on.

54:26.229 --> 54:28.329
MOM: We love you. See you soon. Bye-bye.

